<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>state_machine</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">A<sp/>node<sp/>managing<sp/>the<sp/>robot<sp/>behaviour.<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">It<sp/>receives<sp/>commands<sp/>from<sp/>**user_interface**<sp/>via<sp/>a<sp/>service<sp/>and<sp/>implements<sp/>a<sp/>simple<sp/>finite<sp/>state<sp/>machine.</highlight></codeline>
