<codeline><highlight class="normal">for<sp/>**go_to_point**<sp/>action<sp/>and<sp/>cancel<sp/>the<sp/>goal<sp/>if<sp/>requested.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>random_position_server</highlight></codeline>
