<codeline><highlight class="normal">A<sp/>node<sp/>implementing<sp/>a<sp/>service<sp/>for<sp/>generating<sp/>random<sp/>positions.<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Provides<sp/>the<sp/>**state_machine**<sp/>with<sp/>random<sp/>positions<sp/>for<sp/>**go_to_point**.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>go_to_point</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">A<sp/>node<sp/>implementing<sp/>an<sp/>action<sp/>for<sp/>reaching<sp/>the<sp/>goal<sp/>position<sp/>using<sp/>a<sp/>publisher<sp/>on<sp/>topic<sp/>*/cmd_vel*<sp/>and<sp/>a<sp/>subscriber<sp/>on<sp/>topic<sp/>*/odom*.</highlight></codeline>
